 <title>&kw-hos-tm; 5.0: Backup, Restore, and Disaster Recovery Service (Freezer) Features</title>
 <para>
  Backup, Restore, and Disaster Recovery Service (Freezer) provides integrated
  tools for backing up and restoring cloud data in multiple use cases,
  including disaster recovery. These resources include file systems, server
  instances, volumes, and databases.
 </para>
 <para>
  Freezer is all new for the &kw-hos; Mitaka release.
 </para>
